sub_title: Functional Architect at Energyworx, solving problems in #renewables and #sociotechnicalarchitecture
summary:
I build software with focus on careful and justified architecture, with endless enthusiasm to learn, I'm always trying to use newly acquired knowledge in the workplace.

I'm also a big fan of the functional paradigm and the outdoors.
